    {
      "id": "edge-classes-note-audit-progress",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Current Edge-Class Progress",
      "position": {
        "x": 500,
        "y": 980
      },
      "width": 460,
      "height": 340,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Current Edge-Class Progress\n\nReal work already landed:\n\n- sample edge-class artifacts exist in `/library/classes/edges`\n- edge instances can now carry `data.edgeClassKey`\n- edge classes now own semantic meaning and light render defaults\n- `bridge` now supports `kind: \"edge-class\"`\n- the legend already discovers edge classes from structure\n- the renderer already resolves linked edge-class artifacts and applies render defaults\n\nThe concrete v1 slice now looks like this:\n\n1. formalize the bounded contract\n2. make three starter classes real in authoring\n3. expose them in the legend with a small visual preview\n\nStarter classes:\n\n- `task.depends-on`\n- `planning.answers`\n- `graph.implements`",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
