    {
      "id": "edge-classes-note-gaps",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Remaining Gaps",
      "position": {
        "x": 1000,
        "y": 980
      },
      "width": 440,
      "height": 320,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Remaining Gaps\n\nStill open:\n\n- the v1 edge-class contract still needs to be written down explicitly\n- edge properties still do not treat edge class as the normal semantic authority\n- the legend needs a small class preview so meaning and rendering are exposed together\n- migration/defaulting policy is not settled for unclassed legacy edges\n\nv1 should stay narrow:\n\n- semantic meaning\n- compatibility guidance\n- render defaults\n- legend exposure\n\nNot yet in v1:\n\n- arbitrary runtime behavior\n- execution semantics\n- custom interaction logic",
        "_classBinding": {
